{"tid":418191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［信唔信］扑得越多陰道越鬆？ 婦科專家：同次數無關","createTime":"2017-09-29T10:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T04:39:19.000Z","uid":48083,"like":94,"dislike":482,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"38ceb13de7093cddabea5785f080c360bab83a91","tid":418191,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕「做愛次數越多，陰道會越鬆弛」？有專家表示，這是錯誤的觀念，其實陰道緊實度與做愛次數無關，「即便女性生過小孩，陰道也會在6個月內就恢復正常狀態」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，婦產科博士瑞貝卡（Rebecca Brightman）指出，陰道壁具有彈性、延伸性的組織，女性的陰道鬆緊度在先天在就有差異，每個人都不一樣，並不會因為做愛次數就變鬆，沒辦法以陰道鬆緊度來判斷性經驗豐不豐富。<br />\n<br />\n當男女雙方正在做愛的時候，女方如果很興奮，會使陰道組織膨脹，導致長度、寬度都會增加，男方可能就會覺得不夠緊實，但女生如果處於無聊、緊張的狀態，陰道就會「前後緊貼」，就會讓男生覺得比較緊。<br />\n年齡增長也可能會造成陰道鬆弛，這和肌肉量降低有關，如果女性希望陰道緊實，可以試著運動，可讓陰道的肌肉組織變得緊實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2207912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2207912&d=qSET8glXi%2FJHc%2FxYF9qUzozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9ae35959\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2207912&h=6a4c28ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2207912</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 信<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔信<br />\n<br />\n利申唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e53f0f7ffbb82b0c69cd7b91ac64fb413545b9a","tid":418191,"uid":50663,"like":271,"dislike":8,"score":263,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"個醫生女人黎 你話我信唔信啦"},{"pid":"cfbee52a068a94d0f7c0925bf2ec6f6b1f6c04f0","tid":418191,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:50:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個醫生女人黎 你話我信唔信啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\