5,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:03:04.000Z","msg":"有無生過仔既人出黎講兩句"},{"pid":"34089477c2ec533e3a8207bbcb654f535176eb95","tid":418191,"uid":22585,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:06:13.000Z","msg":"同扑野密度有關，<br />\n<br />\n你試兩2星期唔屌條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d849bfad0ec31d3d294826b2ba0aeb4d1a0b08df","tid":418191,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:07:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係知同毒撚無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266442464bec5d4eb74ad2a18f6ac59166d258bd","tid":418191,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同扑野密度有關，<br />\n<br />\n你試兩2星期唔屌條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要睇年齡<br />\n後生女新陳代謝快<br />\n唔屌一兩星期就緊返<br />\n老女人可以比人屌一獲就反西反足一年"},{"pid":"4b46a433f391eb654005e69eeb92ce10cc517db8","tid":418191,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62ca1c51a8137104f708f015d61f66681090f2e","tid":418191,"uid":123497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:10:22.000Z","msg":"信<br />\n<br />\n利申：巴"},{"pid":"08784773eb7b29f0ab3b617da3fd25a6f57ac5a8","tid":418191,"uid":73804,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:10:44.000Z","msg":"係呀人地醫生都信唔過<br />\n連登仔咩都識"},{"pid":"97fd8577d93be31d5661104ce1f3b49d06f51528","tid":418191,"uid":22553,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160122/780631/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20160122%2F780631%2F&d=qSET8glXi%2FJHc%2FxYF9qUzozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b0a22871\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160122/780631/</a><br />\n台灣高雄一名未婚OL，日前到醫院求診，指原有個下體「大尺寸」男友，換新男友後才知陰道被撐鬆，感受不到「性」福，醫師替她沿陰道壁照射激光，促進膠原蛋白增生，經3次治療後，OL陰道變緊，雖新男友尺寸較小，但已重拾「性」福。<br />\n<br />\n高雄醫院婦產部主治醫生林冠伶指，過去3個月，該部已為90名陰道鬆弛婦女做陰道激光治療。其中7成婦女，是因產後、更年期等，致陰道鬆弛有漏尿等困擾求醫，另外三成是主訴陰道鬆弛、性滿意度低。<br />\n<br />\n林冠伶指，曾有28歲未婚粉領族，為改善性福來做陰道激光治療，她指先前與男友性生活頻繁，換尺寸一般新男友後，她再也無性高潮，新男友也抱怨她的陰道鬆垮垮，做了也無感覺。<br />\n<br />\n高雄醫院婦產部長龍震宇則指，做陰道激光是以鴨嘴器撐開患者陰道，伸入激光探頭沿陰道壁射激光，一次約20分鐘。龍震宇指，陰道有如尿道地基，鬆弛可能降低性滿意度，也易有漏尿困擾，勤練收縮骨盆底肌肉的凱格爾運動可改善，但很多人懶得練，傳統拉緊陰道手術，需住院3天，且疼痛度高。因此，國內外陸續有醫界，以射激光改善陰道鬆弛。依國外報告，約7成尿失禁婦女經激光治療後可改善漏尿，性滿意度也能提升<br />\n比黑鬼屌鬆曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43706dd8f38f7ee1cc5b5c2e4afb3e561956034e","tid":418191,"uid":78971,"like":31,"dislike":6,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:11:33.000Z","msg":"不嬲知<br />\n係上網上到癲撚咗先會信屌到鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁黑鬼屌完你即刻屌就梗係鬆啦<br />\n個閪收窄都收唔切啦"},{"pid":"c30417d91ac04dd504207bf667e891fcbfe8adcd","tid":418191,"uid":28905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"睇留言真係好好笑"},{"pid":"9a92dc671e6c3d29edfa4f17d2c7c609e9f50b90","tid":418191,"uid":28905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:15:12.000Z","msg":"要睇一定睇留言"},{"pid":"cf2504df7f7f90deba5ec745f9e37a29fabf8a13","tid":418191,"uid":5649,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係呀人地醫生都信唔過<br />\n連登仔咩都識</blockquote><br />\n我條女無乜性經驗都好鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登仔唔識就9up"},{"pid":"06cc7cc596d7265a875d8beec